<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 05 at 7:44AM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Travel impacts due to snow this morning...
A brief period of moderate to heavy snow will occur through this
morning, resulting in difficult travel conditions. Snow
accumulations of 1 to 2 inches are expected, but there could be
localized locations of around 3 inches. Visibility may be reduced
to less than one- half mile at times, and roads may become covered
in snow.
Please use caution if you have travel plans in this area this
morning, and consider delaying travel until this afternoon if
possible, when conditions are expected to improve.</description>
